# Never upload secrets to Vercel — env vars are set in the project settings.
#
# WARNING: Vercel's .vercelignore matcher does NOT honor gitignore-style root
# anchoring the way you'd expect. A pattern like "/n8n/" still matched and
# stripped app/api/n8n/ from the build, so the n8n API routes 404'd in prod.
# NEVER exclude by a bare directory name that can collide with a route folder
# (n8n, leads, bots, clients, chat, ...). Exclude by explicit file/glob instead.
#
# The local n8n/ artifacts dir and secrets/ are gitignored already, so CI never
# checks them out; their only sensitive payload is SDR*.json, covered below.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
secrets/*
SDR*.json
docs/ARCHITECTURE.research.json
.vercel
